{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-04156/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-04156"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:41:56"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman puts on a red dress in a crowded dressing room."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-04156","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-04156"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1/a81069de-290c-4b71-84db-90aabaad19f1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:03:42.238Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>As Alma is dressed for the fashion show, her head is covered by a piece of cloth. She is now reminiscent of Reynold’s dress form—not a full person, but just a body, a canvas for Reynold’s art.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:211.8977119784657,119.4347240915209,615.0201884253028,560.7537012113055"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1/7d34bab0-7158-4258-a893-f27922970ce3","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:03:59.539Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The gown that Reynolds dresses Alma in at first is very similar to her <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW115859671 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01334.html\"><u>waitress outfit</u></a>. Likewise, the dress she wears during the fashion show at the House of Woodcock is a more developed version of her original dress. He accentuates her beauty but also keeps her in this subservient role.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04156/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:126.62180349932737,759.0040376850606,777.8196500672948,223.52624495289376"}}}]}]}]}